{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"78d–8","heading":"Annual financial controls audit","label":"78d–8 Annual financial controls audit","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/ch2B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Investor Protection and Securities Reform Act of 2010 and also as part of the Dodd-Frank Wall Street Reform and Consumer Protection Act, and not as part of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 which comprises this chapter.","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection effective 1 day after , except as otherwise provided, see , set out as a note under , Banks and Banking.July 21, 2010section 4 of Pub. L. 111–203section 5301 of Title 12","DefinitionFor definition of “Commission” as used in this section, see , Banks and Banking.section 5301 of Title 12"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Reports of Commission","label":"a Reports of Commission","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Annual reports required","label":"1 Annual reports required","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"describes the responsibility of the management of the Commission for establishing and maintaining an adequate internal control structure and procedures for financial reporting; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"contains an assessment of the effectiveness of the internal control structure and procedures for financial reporting of the Commission during that fiscal year.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Attestation","label":"2 Attestation","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The reports required under paragraph (1) shall be attested to by the Chairman and chief financial officer of the Commission.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Report by Comptroller General","label":"b Report by Comptroller General","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Report required","label":"1 Report required","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the effectiveness of the internal control structure and procedures of the Commission for financial reporting; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the assessment of the Commission under subsection (a)(1)(B).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Attestation","label":"2 Attestation","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Comptroller General shall attest to, and report on, the assessment made by the Commission under subsection (a).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Reimbursements for cost of reports","label":"c Reimbursements for cost of reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Reimbursements required","label":"1 Reimbursements required","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Commission shall reimburse the Government Accountability Office for the full cost of making the reports under subsection (b), as billed therefor by the Comptroller General.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Crediting and use of reimbursements","label":"2 Crediting and use of reimbursements","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fc%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"be credited to the appropriation account “Salaries and Expenses, Government Accountability Office” current when the payment is received; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s78d–8/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs78d%E2%80%938%2Fc%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"remain available until expended.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
